===Alternative forms===
* In Taiwan, the upper component of the character contains {{l|mul|⿻[[一]][[厶]]}} (3 strokes) while in other regions, the upper component contains {{l|mul|⿱[[亠]][[厶]]}} (4 strokes).
* In Taiwan, the bottom component of the character contains {{l|mul|⺼}} (meat radical) while in other regions, the bottom component contains {{l|mul|⺝}} (similar to {{l|mul|月}} but with a vertical left stroke).
* The historical [[w:Kangxi dictionary|Kangxi dictionary]] records two character forms, {{l|mul|⿳[[亠]][[厶]][[⺝]]}} (8 strokes) and {{l|mul|⿱⿻[[一]][[厶]][[⺝]]}} (7 strokes). The alternative form with 7 strokes (page 974, character 10) is based on [[w:Zhengzitong|''Zhengzitong'']] which claims that it is the original form ({{l|zh|本字}}).
* A [[w:CJK Compatibility Ideographs|CJK compatibility ideograph]] exists at <code>U+2F982</code> for the alternative Taiwan form which contains {{l|mul|⿱[[亠]][[厶]]}} (4 strokes) as the upper component and {{l|mul|⺼}} as the bottom component.

